+
+## Common Patterns
+
+### Atomic Commits
+Each commit should:
+- Represent one logical change
+- Be revertable without breaking functionality
+- Include all related changes (code, tests, docs)
+- Pass all tests independently
+
+### Interactive Staging
+For complex changes:
+```bash
