+   
+   **No Examples:**
+   ```ruby
+   # Bad - no usage example
+   # @return [Hash] The result
+   
+   # Good - shows how to use
+   # @return [Hash] The result containing :status and :data
+   # @example
+   #   result = process_data(input)
+   #   puts result[:status]  # => :success
+   #   puts result[:data]    # => { processed: true }
